NAME

DateTime::Locale::kab - Locale data examples for the Kabyle (kab) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Kabyle locale.

Full

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Sḍisass 22 Duǧembeṛ 1995

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Fuṛar 2008

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/2/2008

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10
